result.title: AtCoder Regular Contest 073 / Beginner Contest 060
result.content:
Two contests AtCoder Regular Contest 073 and AtCoder Beginner Contest 060 will be held at the same time.

You can participate in whichever contest you want. (However, you can't register to both competitions.) The last two tasks in ABC are the same as the first two tasks in ARC.

Time： April 29th (Saturday), 21:00 JST

Duration: 100 minutes

Number of Tasks: 4

writer： yosupo

Rating： 0-2799 for ARC, 0-1199 for ABC

The point value are:

ABC: 100 — 200 — 300 — 400

ARC: 300 — 400 — 700 — 900

We are looking forward to your participation!
